productdescription:
Features

  • Bike Pod is a premium product of semi-automatic full body cover of two wheeler vehicle which withstands and repel all of these conditions. At Armad Moteurs, we not only offer a product but we offer a solution to your life problem. We try our very best to develop a relation with our customer by offering after sale service.
    Description
    Bike POD is a semi-automatic vehicle cover which can easily be installed on motorcycle back carrier, other variants can be installed in cars & other vehicle types with few twist to tighten the nuts. With bike POD consumers will have the option to cover their vehicle on the go & save their vehicle against extreme weather conditions like rain, dust etc. It consists of a box which needs to be installed in different places according to the vehicle, fabric is attached with a rotating handle inside the box where it will be rolled in and out of the box, nuts and bolts will be installed as per the requirement of the vehicle. For example, in case of motorcycle it can be attached on the back support carrier handle.

Product Specification

  • High Quality Plastic Is Used
  • Powder Coated Clip & Rotating Handle.
  • Non Sharp Edges
  • 100% Water & Heat Proof Fabric
  • Durable Stitching Of Fabric

How To use Bike Pod

  • Attach Bike Pod To Carrier
  • Tighten Nuts & Bolts
  • Pull Out The Fabric
  • Cover the Bike Fully
  • Make Rope Of Fabric And Rotate The Handle To Put Fabric Back In Devic
